docs {
  # Client — Active oblasts

  Public endpoint. Returns all active oblasts (regions/provinces) sorted by name.

  **Response 200:**
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      { "id": 1, "name": "Ahal" },
      { "id": 2, "name": "Balkan" }
    ]
  }
  ```
}
